title: fanoutqa: How many children does each of the top 5 wealthiest Americans have? (693619f2f644eacd)

chat_history.content: How many children does each of the top 5 wealthiest Americans have?

The top 5 wealthiest people in America are as follows:
1. Elon Musk - 9 children
2. Bill Gates - 3 children
3. Warren Buffett - 3 children
4. Larry Ellison - 2 children
5. Larry Page - 2 children

Let me know if you want to know more about these people.

Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.
